Name: Where Is My Parking Spot
About the game: This is a rage game! Where is my parking spot!? : Drive around parking lots to find your special spot, race against the clock or set a record. You MUST get to that special parking spot! Also... when you use the brakes it also leaks brake fluid? That's normal right? Set new records by going as fast as you can! Try to beat you time per-level and show who's the best! Most levels have secret ways to get faster, try to find them! Times saved to the Steam Cloud! Parking in a spot next to you? NOPE You need that special spot! Park at a store, even on top of a parking garage, and beyond! Parking can be complex and takes skill to master, Up for the challenge? or are you a WIMP?! . Look out for the pesky drivers who love to backup in the parking lot! Make your car look cool. Unlock achievements to earn more skins! Parking has never been cooler, just wait when they see you pull into that spot in style! Paint jobs that make you look so cool, even the parking lots get jealous.
